{
  "texts": [
    "Privacy concerns also hindered group work in technical labs due to the limitations of remote keyboard control features.",
    "Instructors faced challenges in overseeing and reviewing individual student work, which affected instructional capacity.",
    "In general, while the COVID-19 pandemic underscored these challenges, our analysis of the study findings suggests a broader need for adaptive strategies in online learning to address various obstacles and improve educational results.",
    "Despite offering valuable insights, this review has several limitations.",
    "First, the study is limited by the scope of available literature, which may exclude emerging practices and tools not yet widely documented."
  ]
}